{"tid":1516712,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾鎮濤的喪禮(•ᴗ•)","createTime":"2019-08-29T16:03:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T07:07:41.000Z","uid":44730,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"92be63cced514032152808f7ccda2aa27a7173f0","tid":1516712,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:03:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190829/large/1567069900_9456.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190829%2Flarge%2F1567069900_9456.jpg&h=8603e67c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前有份出席撐警活動的鍾鎮濤（阿B），批評年輕人「九唔搭八」，因而惹起忠實fans不滿。之後他有份客串的新片《花椒之味》，戲中他飾演鄭秀文（Sammi）父親。原本阿B在電影宣傳片中有不少鏡頭，但在最新宣傳片中，卻被刪剩2秒。"},{"pid":"0d42115a116d2d44249bdc987d7d743794f8c6ed","tid":1516712,"uid":44730,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:03:46.000Z","msg":"今日電影公司發放新一批有關阿B離世後，舉行喪禮的劇照。只見身為女兒的Sammi以淡妝上陣，披麻帶孝在靈堂上打點，當遇到分別由賴雅妍和李曉峰飾演、兩位來自台灣及大陸同父異母的妹妹時，心情百感交集。而為父親燒衣紙時，三姊妹將全部情緒釋放出來，還大叫着︰「老竇，收嘢呀！」、「老爸，記得收！」她們表示當日一直在哭︰「我們一直哭哭哭，哭到導演喊了『CUT』之後，情緒都依然收不住，三人就繼續擁成一堆，盡情地繼續哭出來了！」"},{"pid":"62154189d1a44e8a3ac924948276bd564232fb23","tid":1516712,"uid":44730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190829/large/1567069900_b1a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190829%2Flarge%2F1567069900_b1a4.jpg&h=562e605f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大女鄭秀文"},{"pid":"38f3d64305fbd250f912b07d2cf1fc2294bf9207","tid":1516712,"uid":98926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:11:57.000Z","msg":"831遊行<br />\n831死線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/npq7Ds0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnpq7Ds0.jpg&h=cd008a46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VggiLqD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVggiLqD.gif&h=29ffb828&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VggiLqD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVggiLqD.gif&h=29ffb828&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VggiLqD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVggiLqD.gif&h=29ffb828&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VggiLqD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVggiLqD.gif&h=29ffb828&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VggiLqD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVggiLqD.gif&h=29ffb828&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VggiLqD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVggiLqD.gif&h=29ffb828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n整咗兩張圖求大家幫手twitter spread出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eC9Jdp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eC9Jdp.png&h=c579fd37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hbqfDMJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbqfDMJ.png&h=fe574e83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一定要通過人權法案<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ec392e05047db6ce70599079cf099630c0588d","tid":1516712,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:31:30.000Z","msg":"鍾鎮濤、彭健新 - 一段情<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UIH52ipX4AU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUIH52ipX4AU&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkC3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=231867d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UIH52ipX4AU</a>"},{"pid":"841c2940b43534a1c8277da71686130eb0e3553d","tid":1516712,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:44:45.000Z","m